          <beat tags="relief, intimacy">As Florence shows concern (color changes signaling welcome, pink for empathy) and addresses applicability to Kira's situation, Kira feels reassured and cared-for. The moment converts procedural interaction into warm connection; the reader feels relief and a sense of intimacy between species.</beat>
          <beat tags="determination, hope">Kira engages with the material, practices reading flower-language, and performs well on the quiz (90%). This is a competence/agency beat—she feels capable and optimistic. The reader experiences satisfaction and renewed hope for her adjustment and recovery.</beat>
        </beats>
